name: World Singles Networks
overview:
World Singles Networks runs leading personals sites like ArabLounge.com, EligibleGreeks.com, IranianPersonals.com and powers online dating and introduction services for leading media brands, online publishers and elite affiliate marketers.

WSN’s approach, technology, and team have been honed by over 10 years of successfully helping millions of people all over the globe, in multiple languages and cultures, connect and find love. World Singles Networks offers its partners winning strategies, best-of-breed technologies, and proven data driven processes for generating revenue.
